title: Yemenia Airways started flight operation in Aden after conflict calmed down
text:
Yemenia Airways started flight operation in Aden after conflict calmed down Adv: 
Aug 06, 2015 Adv: 
Djibouti - Aden on Yemenia Airways. It was the first commercial airline flight operating from and to the Southern Yemeni city of Aden on Thursday. It was the first time since political conflicts erupted 4 months ago. 
Yemenia Airways arrived at 13.00h local time carrying 150 Yemen citizens home after they fled the country.
